{"tid":2328490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國全面脫貧？內部民調打臉：6億人每月僅能吃2次麥當勞","createTime":"2020-12-16T14:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T18:22:57.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b63e86fbf57970e102ab0bc4ee6ff01b5e8668a1","tid":2328490,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"2020/12/16 16:39<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平5年前宣稱要讓中國在2020年「全面脫貧、全面建成小康社會」，中共官方日前高調宣布，中國832個國家級貧困縣「全面脫貧」完成，邁進小康社會，成果舉世矚目。不過，中國社科院11月9日的民調指出，有高達44.4%的中國民眾，過去一年內只花了1,000元人民幣在休閒消費開支上，等於每個月平均只能買兩份麥當勞套餐。<br />\n.....。<br />\n<br />\n對此，《美國之音》報導指出，有專家分析，對照中國總理李克強於6月份所指出的「中國有6億人口的月收入只有1000元人民幣。」中國社科院這份民調代表的是，中國絕大多數人不僅賺得少、基本開銷以外的花費也少，而且貧富差距問題可能相當嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n專家更稱，這都打臉中國官方所宣稱的「中國從今年起已全面脫貧、全面建成小康社會」的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=866255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D866255&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1zizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=1d5ba9cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D866255&h=54d44b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=866255</a>"},{"pid":"fd6d10cdbab54f2dddea780c81901ce406cf4474","tid":2328490,"uid":45232,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"定價過高<br />\n責任全在麥方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb43372bc9ecdfbbed93fa0215c8c1c07d55851","tid":2328490,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd6d10cdbab54f2dddea780c81901ce406cf4474","tid":2328490,"uid":45232,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"定價過高<br />\n責任全在麥方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s